'''Verified group''' is a type of VRChat banner [[Groups|group]], which displays the word "Verified", followed by a noun.

==Origin==

With the release of the [[Groups]] feature released in [[Open Beta]] on November 30th, 2022<ref name="groups-is-here">[https://hello.vrchat.com/blog/vrchat-groups Groups is Now Live! (VRChat blog)]</ref>, and following Elon Musk's purchase<ref>[https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Acquisition_of_Twitter_by_Elon_Musk#Completion_of_purchase Acquisition of Twitter by Elon Musk (Wikipedia)]</ref> of Twitter, Inc. on the month prior, verified groups were created initially to parody Twitter's (now X's) "verified user" badge.

When Twitter was bought out, users who were originally verified with Twitter's famous blue check verification, as well as regular users showed discontent with the introduction of Twitter Blue (now X Premium), making the blue checkmark available to anyone for $8 per month,<ref>[https://techcrunch.com/2022/11/05/twitter-begins-rolling-out-7-99-twitter-blue-plan-with-verification-fewer-ads/ Twitter begins rolling out $7.99 Twitter Blue plan with verification, fewer ads (TechCrunch)]</ref> and followed by mass impersonation by the site's users and becoming a subject of ridicule among internet users.<ref>[https://www.sbnation.com/2022/11/9/23450014/sports-twitter-parody-accounts-elon-musk Sports Twitter is now a verified hellhole thanks to Elon Musk (SBNation)]</ref>

==Notable Examples==

Some groups quickly hit the initial Group member limit of 10,000 set by the developers during the feature's launch. The sudden interest in similar vanity groups with broad appeal was likely{{Citation needed}} part of the reason why the VRChat Team ultimately decided to raise the membership cap to the current limit of 100,000.<ref>[https://help.vrchat.com/hc/en-us/articles/11711571101587-Managing-a-Group Managing a Group (VRChat Help)]</ref>

* '''Verified overthinker'''<ref>[https://vrchat.com/home/group/grp_d9a5a30d-cfd0-4e15-8fcb-ab6945ac1d20 'Verified overthinker'] Group on VRChat; retrieved 11 September, 2024</ref> at 26k+ members
* '''Verified Cutie'''<ref>[https://vrchat.com/home/group/grp_b9bf90ae-c511-4cf8-9853-2f923e1905ea 'Verified Cutie'] Group on VRChat; retrieved 11 September, 2024</ref> at 20k+ members
* '''Verified Problem'''<ref>[https://vrchat.com/home/group/grp_281b5849-6de1-44f5-954e-6072d373764c 'Verified Problem'] Group on VRChat; retrieved 11 September, 2024</ref> at 18k+ members
* '''Verified gremlins'''<ref>[https://vrchat.com/home/group/grp_29c28eac-1cc5-4722-b52f-0221dcb5672a 'Verified gremlins'] Group on VRChat; retrieved 11 September, 2024</ref> at 16k+ members

